https://medium.com/@Alabuja/social-login-in-laravel-with-socialite-90dbf14ee0ab

setup localhost
- tien hanh tao mot application co chuc nang facebook login
  Add New App -> choose setup facebook login -> enter app url:localhost
- In App Domain: enter localhost
- IN Site URL: enter localhost
- IN Facebook Login/settings/Valid OAuth Redirect URIs: enter localhost/facebook/callback( this is
  url for facebook call to your application)


-- google login
--- config
    tien hanh tao mot application theo link sau https://console.developers.google.com/
    tien hanh enable google + API
    thay doi thong tin app hien thi toi user:OAuth consent screen/Application name
    tao credential loaij la Oauth Client Id, applicaiton type la web va setting 2 gia tri nhu sau
        - Authorized JavaScript origins: localhost
        - Authorized redirect URIs: callback url

